This is an Astro website for IloFit, a personal trainer business in Turku, Finland.
- Framework: Astro with Tailwind CSS v4
- Language: Finnish (fi)
- Design: Cormorant Garamond for headings, DM Sans for body
- Brand colors: pink #E8A0B0, charcoal #2D2D2D
- Components live in src/components/, pages in src/pages/
- No React, no JS frameworks — use vanilla JS in <script> tags for interactivity
- Images are in public/images/ as .webp files
